Description: Toom Sara Village - A Breathing Space for Yourself Toom Sara Village is a retreat for souls who love nature and are passionate about exploring ethnic and cultural identities. Discover the Unique Co-tu Cultural Identity Only at Toom Sara Village, Da Nang  Are you seeking a unique and distinctive cultural experience in Quang Nam - Da Nang?  The "Co-tu Show" at 7:30 PM every Saturday at Toom Sara Village is a vibrant and colorful cultural exchange program of the Co-tu ethnic group, one of the long-residing ethnic minorities in the northwestern mountains of Quang Nam province. They have long-standing customs and preserve distinctive traditional cultural values.
